CANVAS DODGER

The aim of the game is to avoid the falling blocks for as long as possible

Collect the power ups to help you succeed further

KEYS:

A or Left arrow - Left
D or Right arrow - Right

W or Up arrow - Toggle up through power ups
S or Down arrow - Toggle down through power ups
Space bar - Use power up

Powerups:

BULLET:
Fires a single bullet to kill the enemy

SHIELD:
Gives you a shield that can take 3 hits. 
Note: Powering up a second shield whilst having an active shield will simply add 3 more lives to the shield

WIPEOUT:
Send a shockwave up the screen to destroy all enemies in sight
